00:09:15,728 --> 00:09:18,371
kuberako ibyo bivuzeko
ntago azagura ibicuruzwa byawe.

204
00:09:18,911 --> 00:09:22,328
ibi twavugagaho nibyo twumvishije
itandukanyirizo.

205
00:09:22,328 --> 00:09:26,108
urabizi, ufite igicuruzwa
byoroshye kugisimbiza.

206
00:09:26,108 --> 00:09:28,109
Uzaba ugifite imyumvire ikomeye,

207
00:09:28,109 --> 00:09:29,777
ushobora kwemeze,

208
00:09:29,777 --> 00:09:31,555
Ariko hari ubundi buryo.

209
00:09:31,555 --> 00:09:33,208
Ni iki abakiriya bakavuze?

210
00:09:33,208 --> 00:09:34,249
Nyine, bakavuze,

211
00:09:34,249 --> 00:09:37,277
