ncobora gukora udahari."

212
00:09:37,277 --> 00:09:40,253
Uzi icyo bivuze, kandi 
bivuzeko udakora igicuruzo.

213
00:09:40,903 --> 00:09:43,786
Cyangwa birakomeye gukora igicuruzwa,
cyakora.

214
00:09:43,786 --> 00:09:46,677
Kandi hanyuma, niba ufite
icyo wasimburisha hanze aho,

215
00:09:46,677 --> 00:09:50,955
urabizi wakavuze,
"imyumvire ikomeye irahari.

216
00:09:50,955 --> 00:09:53,454
Yego, nibikomeye gusimbuzwa birahari."

217
00:09:53,454 --> 00:09:57,254
Ariko ibikomeye kwemezwa
bizatuma abakiriya bavuga,

218
00:09:57,254 --> 00:10:00,062
"Simbyumva neza,
ntago napfa kubikora."

219
00:10:00,062 --> 00:10:01,326
Ibyo bisobanuye iki?

220
00:10:01,326 --> 00:10:04,518
bivuzeko udakora igicuruzo.

221
00:10:04,518 --> 00:10:07,642
Rero niba ufite kimwe muri ibi
ingingo eshatu.

222
00:10:07,642 --> 00:10:09,101
koko uri mubibazo.

223
00:10:09,101 --> 00:10:10,973
rero ufite icyifuzo cyagaciro cyiza,

224
00:10:10,973 --> 00:10:13,182
ibi bintu bitatu byingenzi
bigomba kwerekanwa

225
00:10:13,182 --> 00:10:15,517
rero gerageza ubishake,

226
00:10:15,517 --> 00:10:17,650
kandi ugerageze gukora icyifuzo cyagaciro

227
00:10:17,650 --> 00:10:20,629
ushobora guhitamo
izo ngingo zose uko ari eshatu.

228
00:10:20,629 --> 00:10:22,413
Rero hano hari urugero.

229
00:10:22,413 --> 00:10:25,611
Kandi, hano twujujemo
dukoresheje amakuru

230
00:10:25,611 --> 00:10:29,183
ajyanye na kampani iri gukora
imboni yijisho

231
00:10:29,183 --> 00:10:30,848
yamasoko atandukanye.

232
00:10:30,848 --> 00:10:32,174
Kandi isoma ibingibi,

233
00:10:32,174 --> 00:10:35,326
nkigisubizo cyimboni yijisho,
abakiriya,

234
00:10:35,326 --> 00:10:36,810
bo bashakisha isoko

235
00:10:36,810 --> 00:10:40,385
bari guhura nubushake
bwo kumenya aho abakiriya bareba

236
00:10:40,385 --> 00:10:42,221
mukugura kwabo,

237
00:10:42,221 --> 00:10:46,568
bazashobora kubona ahantu
bareba kubera igiciro,--

238
00:10:46,568 --> 00:10:50,503
reka tubug, nka 50$ kukwezi
mukwiyandikisha,--

239
00:10:50,503 --> 00:10:53,513
kandi ukishimira ibisubizo bitarimo amarangamutima

240
00:10:53,513 --> 00:10:57,870
hamwe namasegonda 20
yo kwitegereza urugendo rwijisho.

241
00:10:58,470 --> 00:11:01,231
bigereranijwe nuburyo
bwo gushaka amakuru,

242
00:11:01,231 --> 00:11:03,353
nko kubaza cyagwa ibibazo,

243
00:11:03,353 --> 00:11:05,069
"Ibyiza
 byo gukoresha ibyo utanga

244
00:11:05,069 --> 00:11:07,459
ni ibisubizo bitagendeye kumarangamutima,

245
00:11:07,459 --> 00:11:10,654
kandi bishobora gutuma
ukora aho ibicuruzwa biba heza

246
00:11:10,654 --> 00:11:12,394
ukoresheje uko ugura.

247
00:11:13,274 --> 00:11:16,736
ibyo ni ibirung
byicyifuzo cyagaciro cyemeza

248
00:11:16,976 --> 00:11:18,584
Nukuri bigerageze kubera ibyo ukora,

249
00:11:18,584 --> 00:11:21,479
kuberako ni ingenzi 
ko wumva

250
00:11:21,479 --> 00:11:23,824
muburyo bwiza
bwibyo ukora ibyo aribyo.

251
00:11:23,824 --> 00:11:25,587
Ibi ni ingenzi,
mugihe uvugana nabakiriya,

252
00:11:25,587 --> 00:11:28,742
abandi bafatanyabikorwa,
nubwoko bwibiganiro,

253
00:11:28,742 --> 00:11:32,793
ibi bizagufasha kuvuga neza
impamvu uri mwiza.

254
00:11:33,093 --> 00:11:36,068
Kandi icyo ni ikintu 
Kampani ntoya zikeneye

255
00:11:36,068 --> 00:11:37,599
binarenze zimwe zikomeye,

256
00:11:37,599 --> 00:11:40,723
Kuberako ugomba kubona
icyo isoko rihagazeho.

257
00:11:41,023 --> 00:11:43,840
ubwo rero wibuke yanteruro imwe
twavuzeho,

258
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,509
kandi wibuke
gusubiramo.

259
00:11:45,889 --> 00:11:48,231
Icyifuzo cyagaciro cyiza
kigomba kumvikanisha,

260
00:11:48,231 --> 00:11:51,422
kigomba gutandukanya,
